    <item>
      <title>Altice 债权人提出的计划可能导致德拉希失去控制权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/altice-creditors-propose-plan-that-could-see-drahi-lose-control</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，Altice France 的一大批担保债权人向该公司发送了一份提案，要求解决其 244 亿欧元（合 272 亿美元）的债务问题，这增加了亿万富翁老板帕特里克·德拉希 (Patrick Drahi) 失去控制权的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/altice-creditors-propose-plan-that-could-see-drahi-lose-control</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 15:22:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>垃圾债券投资者正在领先于“降息派对”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/junk-bond-investors-are-getting-ahead-of-rate-cutting-party</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储即将降息，正推动美国公司债券市场风险最高的领域出现反弹，但一些投资者担心这股热潮可能不会持续。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/junk-bond-investors-are-getting-ahead-of-rate-cutting-party</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 15:15:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约市交通系统计划斥资 654 亿美元升级中央车站和地铁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/ny-s-mta-plans-65-4-billion-of-system-upgrades-to-subways-rail-lines</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约市交通系统计划在未来五年内投资 654 亿美元，购买数千辆火车车厢、升级变电站、翻新中央车站火车站并加固车站和轨道以抵御极端天气。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/ny-s-mta-plans-65-4-billion-of-system-upgrades-to-subways-rail-lines</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 15:15:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通、瑞银加入国际清算银行基于区块链的跨境支付改革计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/jpmorgan-ubs-join-bis-blockchain-based-plan-to-overhaul-cross-border-payments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际清算银行已与全球一些最大的银行和信用卡公司合作开展一个基于区块链的项目，旨在彻底改革全球跨境支付。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/jpmorgan-ubs-join-bis-blockchain-based-plan-to-overhaul-cross-border-payments</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 15:09:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>SEC 批准对股票定价和交易费用进行改革</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/sec-poised-to-vote-on-overhaul-of-stock-pricing-exchange-fees</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国证券交易委员会已批准相关规则，允许交易所交易的数千只股票和 ETF 以半美分增量进行报价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/sec-poised-to-vote-on-overhaul-of-stock-pricing-exchange-fees</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>罗杰斯以 35 亿美元的价格控制枫叶队和猛龙队</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/rogers-buys-3-5-billion-maple-leaf-sports-stake-sportico-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗杰斯通讯公司 (Rogers Communications Inc.) 以 47 亿加元（35 亿美元）收购了 BCE 公司所持有的枫叶体育娱乐有限公司 (Maple Leaf Sports &amp; Entertainment Ltd.) 37.5% 的股份，从而使这家电信巨头获得了该体育公司的多数股权，该公司最有价值的资产包括 NHL 的多伦多枫叶队和 NBA 的多伦多猛龙队。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/rogers-buys-3-5-billion-maple-leaf-sports-stake-sportico-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 12:28:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
